<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_C1F219E622044D43852EF5168FF7192A"> 
  <title>Classification Rule Builder</title> 
  <shortdesc>Rather than maintaining and uploading classifications each time
	 your tracking codes change, you can create automatic, rule-based
	 classifications and apply them across multiple report suites. Rules are
	 processed at frequent intervals, depending on your volume of classification
	 related traffic. 
  </shortdesc> 
  <prolog> 
	 <metadata> 
		<othermeta name="solution" content="Analytics"/> 
		<othermeta name="topic" content="Admin tools"/> 
		<othermeta name="subtopic" content="Classifications"/> </metadata>
  </prolog> 
  <conbody> 
	 <section id="section_3FF666EF9D5B4E37A23B3FB400CDA2E6"> 
		<title>Getting Started with Classification Rules</title> 
		<p> 
		  <uicontrol>Admin tools</uicontrol> &gt; 
		  <uicontrol>Classifications</uicontrol> &gt; 
		  <uicontrol>Rule Builder</uicontrol> 
		</p> 
		<p>Here are the high-level steps you take to classification rules: 
		</p> 
		<table id="table_DF3A0DFCA34C4A40BD7930E07FB28C00"> 
		  <tgroup cols="4"> 
			 <colspec colname="col01" colnum="1" colwidth="1.00*"/> 
			 <colspec colnum="2" colname="col1" colwidth="1.89*"/> 
			 <colspec colname="col02" colnum="3" colwidth="1.85*"/> 
			 <colspec colnum="4" colname="col2" colwidth="3.53*"/> 
			 <thead> 
				<row> 
				  <entry colname="col01">Step 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col1">Task 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col02">Location 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col2">Description 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
			 </thead> 
			 <tbody> 
				<row> 
				  <entry colname="col01"> 
					 <p><image href="graphics/step1_icon.png"
						id="image_2B9410A896C64591A852DD0FFE5CB1BA"><?xm-replace_text Paragraph?></image>
						
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col1"> 
					 <p>(Prerequisite) 
						<xref
						 href="https://marketing.adobe.com/resources/help/en_US/reference/index.html?f=classifications"
						 format="https" scope="external">Classify your variables</xref>. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col02"> 
					 <wintitle>Admin Tools</wintitle> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col2"> 
					 <p>Variables must have at least one classification column
						created before they are available for use in rules. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
				<row>
				  <entry colname="col01">
					 <p><image href="graphics/step2_icon.png"
						id="image_D19C29A109C844E598E7343E89E92B88"><?xm-replace_text Paragraph?></image>
						
					 </p>
				  </entry>
				  <entry colname="col1">
					 <p>Specify the report suite to scan for classified variables
					 </p>
				  </entry>
				  <entry colname="col02"><wintitle>Admin Tools</wintitle>
				  </entry>
				  <entry colname="col2">
				  </entry>
				</row>
				<row> 
				  <entry colname="col01">
					 <p><image href="graphics/step3_icon.png"
						id="image_EDD01A95F5D7427A9AA97EA713735083"><?xm-replace_text Paragraph?></image>
						
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col1"> 
					 <p> 
						<xref
						 href="t_classification_rule_set.xml#task_86F216DFD2534FA181E64ABDF306782B"
						 format="dita" scope="local">Create a rule set</xref>. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col02"> 
					 <wintitle>Rule Builder</wintitle> Page 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col2"> 
					 <p>Create a rule set and apply the set to a variable. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
				<row> 
				  <entry colname="col01">
					 <p><image href="graphics/step4_icon.png"
						id="image_6F19EBE7EDAF458A86E529247D9ECCB1"><?xm-replace_text Paragraph?></image>
						
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col1"> 
					 <p> 
						<xref
						 href="classification_quickstart_rules.xml#concept_CF2F64BD96454FBFAA84638FC7DEA263"
						 format="dita" scope="local">Add classification rules to the set</xref>. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col02"> 
					 <wintitle>Rules</wintitle> Page 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col2"> 
					 <p>Match a condition to a classification, and then specifying
						the action to take for the rule. 
					 </p> 
					 <p>Be familiar with the information in 
						<xref
						 href="about_classification_rules.xml#concept_A67A23F523844D37898583C632DB9D25"
						 format="dita" scope="local"><?xm-replace_text About Classification Rules?></xref>.
						
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
				<row> 
				  <entry colname="col01">
					 <p><image href="graphics/step5_icon.png"
						id="image_061EB089A8EF4165B6A81CC645F2B43A"><?xm-replace_text Paragraph?></image>
						
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col1"> 
					 <p> 
						<xref
						 href="t_classifications_test_rule.xml#task_618A1E7CC8664E728F312250E8367158"
						 format="dita" scope="local"> <?xm-replace_text Test a classification rule set?>
						</xref>. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col02"> 
					 <p> 
						<wintitle>Testing</wintitle> Page 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col2"> 
					 <p>You will want to test rules for validation by editing them
						in Draft mode. In Draft mode, rules cannot run. 
					 </p> 
					 <p> This step is important when using 
						<xref
						 href="regex_classification_rules.xml#concept_8A63F9BCF9484963962E14E6286D312D"
						 format="dita" scope="local">regular expressions</xref>. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
				<row> 
				  <entry colname="col01">
					 <p><image href="graphics/step6_icon.png"
						id="image_0F2AD6AE741D4B63A9B69CD1EBCCB8B1"><?xm-replace_text Paragraph?></image>
						
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col1"> 
					 <p> 
						<xref
						 href="classification_rule_definitions.xml#concept_6CAEFB1CA4564E2CA5808097C11EF468/section_4A5BF384EEEE4994B6DC888339833529"
						 format="dita" scope="local">Activate valid rules</xref>. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col02"> 
					 <wintitle>Rules</wintitle> Page 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col2"> 
					 <p>Once rules are valid, activate the rule set. 
					 </p> 
					 <p>You can overwrite existing keys, if necessary. See 
						<xref
						 href="about_classification_rules.xml#concept_A67A23F523844D37898583C632DB9D25"
						 format="dita" scope="local"><?xm-replace_text How Rules Are Processed?></xref>.
						
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
				<row> 
				  <entry colname="col01">
					 <p><image href="graphics/step7_icon.png"
						id="image_89BFBE52C55044D08F27F9C0B6040F3F"></image>
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col1"> 
					 <p>(Optional) 
						<xref
						 href="classification_rule_definitions.xml#concept_6CAEFB1CA4564E2CA5808097C11EF468/section_4A5BF384EEEE4994B6DC888339833529"
						 format="dita" scope="local">Delete unwanted rules</xref>. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col02"> 
					 <p> 
						<wintitle>Rules</wintitle> Page 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="col2"> 
					 <p>Delete unwanted rules from a set. 
					 </p> 
					 <note>Deleting rules does not delete classified data uploaded. 
					 </note> 
					 <p>See 
						<xref
						 href="t_delete_classification_data.xml#task_105C3761180A4D21B8395730C39B5F89"
						 format="dita" scope="local"><?xm-replace_text Delete classification data?></xref>
						if you need to delete classified data. 
					 </p> 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
			 </tbody> 
		  </tgroup> 
		</table> 
		<note>Groups with permissions to use the classification import tool can
		  use classification rules. See 
		  <xref
			href="about_classification_rules.xml#concept_A67A23F523844D37898583C632DB9D25"
			format="dita" scope="local"><?xm-replace_text How Rules Are Processed?></xref>
		  for important processing information. 
		</note> 
